{"id":563,"category_slug":"toefl-listening","category_name":"TOEFL Listening","position":13,"title":"TOEFL Conversation 7","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":74,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toefl-listening/toefl-conversation-7.563/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/0-conversation-7.mp3","transcript":"Can I help you?\nAre you looking for something in particular?\nYes, well... first I'm looking for the foreign language section.\nOh, it's right down here.\nHere we are. \"Foreign Languages\".\nWhat course are you taking?\nSpanish Four Thirty-one.\nYou need the Intermediate Spanish textbook?\nNo, I still have that from Four Thirty.\nWhat I'm looking for is the novel we're supposed to read:\nGarcia Marquez's 'Cien años de soledad',\n'One Hundred Years of Solitude'.\n'Garcia Marquez', 'Garcia Marquez'. Hmm. No...\nOh, here it is, under 'Marquez'.\nHere you are.\nEighteen dollars?\nThe price is right, but, erm, it's just the text.\nThere doesn't seem to be any footnotes or any glossary.\nAh.\nThis is the only edition you have?\nYes, it is. Sorry.\nHmm. How many copies do you have left?\nJust those on the shelf?\nYes, uh, four, no, five copies.\nJeez, those'll be gone by Friday for sure.\nOur class is really full.\nWhat's your return policy?\nWould it be OK if I bought this now,\nand then returned it if I can find an annotated edition on the internet?\nYes, certainly.\nBut you'll need to keep your receipt, of course,\nand be sure that the book is not marked up or damaged in any way.\nSure, that's fair enough.\nDid you want me to check whether we can find you another edition?\nI don't think I have time.\nIt usually takes so long to get a book through a bookstore.\nHaha, unfortunately, that's often true.\nThanks anyway.\nI'll take this then, and say, you have, uh, sweatshirts, don't you?\nSweatshirts? Yes, in the 'School Spirit' section.\nOver this way. And down here. Um...\nHere you are.\nAh. Yes.\nHmm... that's not much of a school crest.\nOh. There's a bigger one on the back, see?\nOh, yeah, of course. I see.\nUh, this is a medium.\nI need a large, and uh... I think... in green.\nMedium, medium... here, is this a large?\nYes, large. Here you go.\nYeah, that's good.\nSay, do you know what our motto means, anyway?\n\"Ex Pertinacia Veritas\".\n\"Out of something... something-or-other\".\n\"From Determination comes Truth\".\nIt's been SU's motto since it was founded in 1894.\nAnd this crest is \"an American bison couchant upon a tome vert\".\nWhat in heck does that mean?\nA buffalo lying on a green book.\nI think the idea was that this new pioneer state was getting its first institution of higher education,\nthe buffalo represents the prairies,\nthe green of the book, and the book represents learning.\nHuh. That's really interesting.\nI'll wear it with pride, and hope for some of that determination!\nHow much is this?\n39.95 plus tax.\nFine.\nUh, what else do I need now?\nMmm... I guess that's it, then: the sweatshirt and the book.\nAnd there's no tax on the book.\nWhere's your register?\nJust take them up to the cashier at the front, please. Over there.\nOh, OK. Thanks a lot for your help.\nThank you. Have a nice day.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:59:09","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Can I help you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/1.mp3","time_start":6.87,"time_end":7.95},{"position":2,"content":"Are you looking for something in particular?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/2.mp3","time_start":8.23,"time_end":10.37},{"position":3,"content":"Yes, well... first I'm looking for the foreign language section.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/3.mp3","time_start":10.87,"time_end":15.11},{"position":4,"content":"Oh, it's right down here.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/4.mp3","time_start":15.28,"time_end":16.99},{"position":5,"content":"Here we are. \"Foreign Languages\".","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/5.mp3","time_start":17.05,"time_end":19.11},{"position":6,"content":"What course are you taking?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/6.mp3","time_start":19.25,"time_end":20.89},{"position":7,"content":"Spanish Four Thirty-one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/7.mp3","time_start":21.23,"time_end":23.37},{"position":8,"content":"You need the Intermediate Spanish textbook?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/8.mp3","time_start":23.61,"time_end":26.43},{"position":9,"content":"No, I still have that from Four Thirty.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/9.mp3","time_start":26.71,"time_end":29.47},{"position":10,"content":"What I'm looking for is the novel we're supposed to read:","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/10.mp3","time_start":29.59,"time_end":32.6},{"position":11,"content":"Garcia Marquez's 'Cien años de soledad',","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/11.mp3","time_start":32.75,"time_end":36.47},{"position":12,"content":"'One Hundred Years of Solitude'.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/12.mp3","time_start":36.63,"time_end":38.81},{"position":13,"content":"'Garcia Marquez', 'Garcia Marquez'. Hmm. No...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/13.mp3","time_start":39.01,"time_end":43.47},{"position":14,"content":"Oh, here it is, under 'Marquez'.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/14.mp3","time_start":43.55,"time_end":45.44},{"position":15,"content":"Here you are.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/15.mp3","time_start":45.53,"time_end":46.4},{"position":16,"content":"Eighteen dollars?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/16.mp3","time_start":46.75,"time_end":48.27},{"position":17,"content":"The price is right, but, erm, it's just the text.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/17.mp3","time_start":48.37,"time_end":52.23},{"position":18,"content":"There doesn't seem to be any footnotes or any glossary.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/18.mp3","time_start":52.36,"time_end":55.75},{"position":19,"content":"Ah.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/19.mp3","time_start":55.97,"time_end":56.93},{"position":20,"content":"This is the only edition you have?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/20.mp3","time_start":57.55,"time_end":59.84},{"position":21,"content":"Yes, it is. Sorry.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/21.mp3","time_start":59.92,"time_end":61.49},{"position":22,"content":"Hmm. How many copies do you have left?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/22.mp3","time_start":61.77,"time_end":64.85},{"position":23,"content":"Just those on the shelf?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/23.mp3","time_start":6