ydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/33.mp3","time_start":92.61,"time_end":94.4},{"position":34,"content":"Did you want me to check whether we can find you another edition?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/34.mp3","time_start":94.57,"time_end":97.53},{"position":35,"content":"I don't think I have time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/35.mp3","time_start":97.88,"time_end":99.63},{"position":36,"content":"It usually takes so long to get a book through a bookstore.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/36.mp3","time_start":99.76,"time_end":103.11},{"position":37,"content":"Haha, unfortunately, that's often true.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/37.mp3","time_start":103.29,"time_end":106.37},{"position":38,"content":"Thanks anyway.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/38.mp3","time_start":106.59,"time_end":107.76},{"position":39,"content":"I'll take this then, and say, you have, uh, sweatshirts, don't you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/39.mp3","time_start":107.92,"time_end":112.51},{"position":40,"content":"Sweatshirts? Yes, in the 'School Spirit' section.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/40.mp3","time_start":112.67,"time_end":116.19},{"position":41,"content":"Over this way. And down here. Um...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/41.mp3","time_start":116.39,"time_end":119.59},{"position":42,"content":"Here you are.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/42.mp3","time_start":119.8,"time_end":120.84},{"position":43,"content":"Ah. Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/43.mp3","time_start":121.13,"time_end":122.65},{"position":44,"content":"Hmm... that's not much of a school crest.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/44.mp3","time_start":122.81,"time_end":125.61},{"position":45,"content":"Oh. There's a bigger one on the back, see?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/45.mp3","time_start":126.41,"time_end":129.43},{"position":46,"content":"Oh, yeah, of course. I see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/46.mp3","time_start":129.69,"time_end":132.16},{"position":47,"content":"Uh, this is a medium.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/47.mp3","time_start":132.31,"time_end":134.08},{"position":48,"content":"I need a large, and uh... I think... in green.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/48.mp3","time_start":134.08,"time_end":137.49},{"position":49,"content":"Medium, medium... here, is this a large?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/49.mp3","time_start":137.68,"time_end":141.03},{"position":50,"content":"Yes, large. Here you go.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/50.mp3","time_start":141.19,"time_end":143.23},{"position":51,"content":"Yeah, that's good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/51.mp3","time_start":143.45,"time_end":144.8},{"position":52,"content":"Say, do you know what our motto means, anyway?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/52.mp3","time_start":144.93,"time_end":148.05},{"position":53,"content":"\"Ex Pertinacia Veritas\".","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/53.mp3","time_start":148.17,"time_end":150.56},{"position":54,"content":"\"Out of something... something-or-other\".","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/54.mp3","time_start":150.76,"time_end":153.49},{"position":55,"content":"\"From Determination comes Truth\".","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/55.mp3","time_start":153.64,"time_end":156.01},{"position":56,"content":"It's been SU's motto since it was founded in 1894.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/56.mp3","time_start":156.17,"time_end":160.03},{"position":57,"content":"And this crest is \"an American bison couchant upon a tome vert\".","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/57.mp3","time_start":160.21,"time_end":164.84},{"position":58,"content":"What in heck does that mean?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/58.mp3","time_start":165.17,"time_end":167.4},{"position":59,"content":"A buffalo lying on a green book.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/59.mp3","time_start":167.55,"time_end":169.84},{"position":60,"content":"I think the idea was that this new pioneer state was getting its first institution of higher education,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/60.mp3","time_start":169.91,"time_end":176.48},{"position":61,"content":"the buffalo represents the prairies,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/61.mp3","time_start":176.63,"time_end":178.89},{"position":62,"content":"the green of the book, and the book represents learning.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/62.mp3","time_start":179.07,"time_end":182.32},{"position":63,"content":"Huh. That's really interesting.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/63.mp3","time_start":182.65,"time_end":185.16},{"position":64,"content":"I'll wear it with pride, and hope for some of that determination!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/64.mp3","time_start":185.29,"time_end":188.89},{"position":65,"content":"How much is this?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/65.mp3","time_start":189.09,"time_end":190.43},{"position":66,"content":"39.95 plus tax.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/66.mp3","time_start":190.81,"time_end":193.4},{"position":67,"content":"Fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/67.mp3","time_start":193.61,"time_end":194.39},{"position":68,"content":"Uh, what else do I need now?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/68.mp3","time_start":194.56,"time_end":196.67},{"position":69,"content":"Mmm... I guess that's it, then: the sweatshirt and the book.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/69.mp3","time_start":196.67,"time_end":200.33},{"position":70,"content":"And there's no tax on the book.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/70.mp3","time_start":200.51,"time_end":202.4},{"position":71,"content":"Where's your register?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/71.mp3","time_start":202.57,"time_end":204.11},{"position":72,"content":"Just take them up to the cashier at the front, please. Over there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/72.mp3","time_start":204.11,"time_end":207.48},{"position":73,"content":"Oh, OK. Thanks a lot for your help.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/73.mp3","time_start":207.67,"time_end":210.64},{"position":74,"content":"Thank you. Have a nice day.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toefl-listening/conversation-7-2023-01-22-22-37-09/74.mp3","time_start":210.8,"time_end":212.91}]}